| connectors.sch | Renamed GLabel HP_DP_38_N → FMC_H32_LA28_N on J1-B37 stub at (5400,7150) |
| adrv9009_signals.sch | Reverted DEC-030 GLabels: removed 4 GLabels, restored original floating wires + notes |

