| connectors.sch | 1 (VIN, new) | 0 | 8 power nets via JX pins | VIN fixed; others have global LDO drivers |
| power.sch | 6 | 26 | VIN+5 output rails | All locally driven |
| adrv9009_signals.sch | 0 | 0 | None | No power symbols, no risk |
| support_io.sch | 0 | 5 | GND only (now connected) | GND: global net; no risk |

