Unchanged:
  - Zero-tolerance-on-correctness, startup-speed-on-everything-else.
  - All working discipline (per-edit approval, atomic Python edits,
    primary sources arbitrate, on-disk artifact + MD5 is ground
    truth, no GUI edits to files, no bash heredocs to project
    files).
  - All open technical defects (DEF-11 closure pending topology
    verification, DEC-038 I2C tie held, potential DEF-14
